                     <interp inst="t18220417-151-off785" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220417-151-cd786" type="crimeDate">14th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220417-151-off785 t18220417-151-cd786"></join>, one bushel of pollard and beans mixed together, value 1 s., and one sack, value 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220417-151-victim1451" type="victimName">
                     James 
